Package bike.products

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Buyable
    An interface to represent anything that may be purchased.
    Rentable
    An interface to represent anything that may be rented out for an hourly fee.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Accessory
    A class to represent an accessory sold at a shop.
    AirPump

    BMX
    A representation of a BMX bike being rented from a shop.
    Cost
    The Cost class represents all money objects with integer values.

    A representation of a beach cruiser bicycle being rented from a shop.

    Light

    MountainBike
    A representation of a mountain bike being rented from a shop.
    Product
    A class to represent a product sold at the shop.
    TandemBike
    A representation of a tandem bike being rented from a shop.
    Unicycle
    A representation of a unicycle being rented from a shop.
